// ============================================================
// IFC — Institutional Flourishing Capital (Wave 11).
// Defines how institutional flourishing is represented,
// measured, accumulated, protected and connected to
// Intelligence. Additive only — reuses D13/D14/D16/D17/D18/
// D19/FIC/IUC/USFIP by reference (no FK, no duplicated logic).
